def create_user(user: schemas.UserCreate, db: Session = Depends(get_db)):
    hashed_password = utils.hash(user.password)
    user.password = hashed_password
    new_user = models.User(
        **user.dict(),
    )
    db.add(new_user)
    db.commit()
    db.refresh(new_user)
    return new_user
